{"tid":1000202,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人生第一次坐廉航，唔會再有第二次","createTime":"2019-01-29T09:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T09:29:12.000Z","uid":181685,"like":2,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f0b741ba07671e2e578a51fbf52b588ae6178a07","tid":1000202,"uid":181685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T09:15:59.000Z","msg":"話說早幾日去旅行。匆匆忙咁去左fk express到買機票。<br />\n因為第一次係呢到買乜都唔知，我以為會好似平時咁.乜都包哂你。<br />\n到我check in個日，出事啦！<br />\n仆你個街.我拎住成個gip要我加錢寄艙。不過好彩我去個時唔多野。<br />\n仲要冇都揀位坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到上機，屌那星，飲杯水都要比錢.大佬我坐成3-4個鐘架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要冇飯食.又要比錢<br />\n咁搞法我正常買張機票都仲平撚過佢<br />\n到我走個日，個gip 超重.焗住比成500蚊由7kg up到20kg<br />\n我發誓唔會再買廉航。屌你老味"},{"pid":"9d23d0dc481dc970ad363a9fe45d6cd5c6aef462","tid":1000202,"uid":20449,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T09:16:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da76116632c6a414b2008f32ac37e6a88d4991f8","tid":1000202,"uid":33730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T09:17:30.000Z","msg":"樓主假膠得太過火"},{"pid":"6d3146f27a9399988234ddcb3e18080f0bb852da","tid":1000202,"uid":16034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T09:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死窮撚坐廉航又要拎gip <br />\n明明買飛個時講明得7kg hand carry又唔買"},{"pid":"7def9168185ab44f04cc50af64c89398fbb35541","tid":1000202,"uid":98387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T09:17:45.000Z","msg":",你問題"},{"pid":"19a15fbc0c2d3f99900108bb22e5a2f53e508c95","tid":1000202,"uid":2959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T09:18:34.000Z","msg":"自己唔睇清楚就買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef086262599190bb0978af5fb7fe20bf3fdd2